
1. Download the repo from github.
In MATLAB:- 
2. Add the "Speaker Recognition" folder to the path.
3. Go to the "Classification_Speaker_Recognition" folder. Basically, the root folder
4. To run the main implementation, write "run implementation1.m" in the MATLAB command line.
5. To run the BIC based classification, write "run implementation_bic.m" in the MATLAB command line.
